(8, 4, '2015-08-08 09:40:31', '2015-08-08 09:40:31', '<h1>About Us</h1>\r\n<p class="highlight">Every day many of the world''s most trusted companies¬†put their faith in Omega to ensure the integrity of their global supply chains as they endeavor to work with partners who are ethical,¬†secure¬†and free from corrupt practices.</p>\r\nOmega goes beyond monitoring. We focus upon thorough¬†assessments, comprehensive¬†investigations, full disclosure and effective remediation. We strive to ensure that all parties, from manufacturers, trading entities, logistics providers, brands and retailers have full transparency over their supply chain partners, product and associates. We enable our clients to understand any shortcomings then provide them with the expertise to remediate effectively allowing them to operate their supply chains with complete confidence.', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2016-03-23 23:11:33', '2016-03-24 07:11:33', '', 0, 'http://local.omega.com/?page_id=8', 0, 'page', '', 0),
