 business, please contact us.', 'How Do I Prevent Bribery Across My Supply Base?', 'Consumer brands and retailers have clear regulations governing unethical supply chain practices within their own organizations.¬† However, very few have equivalent procedures for managing cases of bribery involving external partners.  This is a major blind spot. ', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '254-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-27 22:40:57', '2016-01-28 06:40:57', '', 254, 'https://local.omega.com/254-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
