nd Laos.\r\n\r\nIdentifying and remediating forced labor is a complex issue. Omega has vast experience in dealing with the challenge. For more information, please <a href="https://local.omega.com/contact/" target="_blank">contact us</a>.', 'How Exposed Is My Supply Chain to Forced Labor??', 'Forced labor has never been more topical. The subject is complex. ¬†Forced labor comes in many forms and exposure to the issue, and how you mitigate risk, is dependent on the industry you operate in as well as the nature of your supply chain.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '299-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-07 22:17:53', '2016-03-08 06:17:53', '', 299, 'https://local.omega.com/299-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
