le Sourcing: How Do I Measure Success?', 'Responsible sourcing programs require significant investment in both time and dollars.  How does your organization measure the success of its program should it be challenged by either leadership or external stakeholders?', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '422-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-26 04:36:38', '2016-09-26 12:36:38', '', 422, 'https://local.omega.com/422-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
